Name: Void Source
About the game: Features Levels full of non-stop action, including highly hazardous environments: Underwater, Volcano, Space, Dark Cave, Railroad Huge bosses that pack a punch. Boss rush extra mode. Optional scanline screen FX, as seen in trailer. 25 weapons (two same weapons stack up to higher power). Steam Trading Cards. Steam Achievements. Dozens of new weapons, developed via technology tree between the levels. Lead Programmer - Xitilon Programmer and Visual Designer - Lowixsama Music and Sound - Darkman007 Concept and Visual Designer - Satterion Trailer - Lowixsama Greenlight Trailer - Dr. Z10
